<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Not at all. I would recommend this book; it&apos;s a classic I have read several times. I think you&apos;re taking it too literally; some of the best books requ<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Not at all. I would recommend this book; it's a classic I have read several times. I think you're taking it too literally; some of the best books require a suspension of disbelief. Think of it as an allegory.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
